Package: picam-webcam
Version: 1.0-1
Section: video
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-flask, python3-picamera2, python3-opencv, python3-gevent, python3-numpy, ffmpeg
Maintainer: Jack Knight <jfk@linux.com>
Description: PiCam Motion Webcam with Flask and Picamera2
 A headless, non-blocking motion detection webcam server 
 for Raspberry Pi using Picamera2, OpenCV, and Gevent.

